{"id":418130,"date":[{"year":1961,"month":5,"day":21}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"276","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我们找到了光明","ftitle":"","authors":["徐太行"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐太行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载:日本盲人鹤田在其他三位盲人的帮助下，经半年努力，带病把毛泽东著作《实践论》和《矛盾论》译成点字本，供日本全国二十五万盲人摸读。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是贫困失业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是饥寒疾病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是长崎广岛的原子烟尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺去了你的光明?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是主子的皮鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是吉普的吼声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是持刀阔步的东条亡魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震扰着你的心灵?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是时代的步履，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是北京的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是祖国樱花的芳芬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切地把你招引?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……因而，你啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黑暗中不畏惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在寒冷中不颤慄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在疾病中不呻吟…"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你打开心灵之窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接中国的太阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——用喜悦的激动的双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧着毛泽东的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大声地向日本盲人喊道:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们找到了光明!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明!!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明!!!"}]}